    oc:hasDescription "Migrate Spring Security 5 to Spring Security 6 configuration. Use when removing WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter, replacing @EnableGlobalMethodSecurity with @EnableMethodSecurity, converting antMatchers to requestMatchers, or updating to lambda DSL configuration style. Covers SecurityFilterChain beans and authentication manager changes." ;
